_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"성의 극약","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"성공적인 젊은 샐러리맨 카츠나기는 한 순간의 부주의함으로 인해 부모와 모든 것을 잃고 나락으로 떨어져 급기야 자살을 시도한다. 미지의 남자 요덴이 그의 목숨을 구하지만, 카츠나기는 어딘지 알 수 없는 곳에 사슬에 묶여 감금된 자신을 발견한다. 그리고 요덴은 카츠나기의 몸 이곳 저곳을 탐색하며 끊임없는 성적 고문을 자행한다. 영문도 모른 채 묶인 채 카츠나기는 점차 고통에 익숙해져 가는 자신을 발견하고, 두 사람의 기이한 관계 뒤에는 또 다른 비밀이 숨어 있었다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"性之剧毒","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"改编自畅销同名BL漫画，讲述了一名原本生活完美的精英男，意外失去所有——父母、事业、未婚妻。丧失继续活下去的勇气，生无可恋的他藉着醉意，意图跳楼自杀。之后遇到男二，并一步步地爱上了他的故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":89,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://seino-gekiyaku.com/","overview":"「俺のせいで、すべてが無くなった…」\r 完璧な人生から転落したエリートサラリーマンの桂木は、絶望のさなか酔った勢いで飛び降り自殺をはかる。\r 「捨てるなら…その命、俺に寄こせ!」\r 突然現れた謎の男・余田に助けられるのだが、それは恐ろしい監禁調教生活のはじまりだった…"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Dangerous Drugs of Sex","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"[SUB ITA] Makoto Katsuragi è dirigente che pa causa della morte improvvisa dei genitori, viene lasciato dalla fidanzata ed è costretto a dimettersi dal lavoro. Sotto l'effetto dell'alcool, decide di suicidarsi, ma subito prima di potersi lanciare da un edificio, viene salvato da un uomo misterioso di nome Ryūji Yoden. Quest'ultimo lo trasforma in uno schiavo obbligandolo a una vita di reclusione e iniziandolo al sadomasochismo. Katsuragi si innamora di Yoden e riconsidera il proposito di suicidarsi. Il film è tratto dal famosissimo manga \"Dangerous Sex: The Indecently Developed Body\" di Yuki Mizuta."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"性之劇藥","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"原本有個完美人生的菁英上班族桂木，卻一夕之間失去所有，在酒醉又絕望下想一了百了。「如果你想要捨棄這條命的話，那就把他交給我吧！」突然出現一位神秘男子余田的幫忙，但卻也沒想到這是監禁調教生活的開始..."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Dangerous Drugs of Sex","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"性之劇藥","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"原本有個完美人生的菁英上班族桂木，卻一夕之間失去所有，在酒醉又絕望下想一了百了。「如果你想要捨棄這條命的話，那就把他交給我吧！」突然出現一位神秘男子餘田的幫忙，但卻也沒想到這是監禁調教生活的開始. . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1493425,"adult":false,"title":"Morgan: Killer Doll","video":false,"overview":"Things go awry when Astrid doesn't share the same feelings for her longtime best friend, Darcy.","genre_ids":[27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5395,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/eZaITue9TqLzxILtiunBoQ448Pd.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-13","vote_average":5.758,"backdrop_path":"/jfSjAU29orZXCDgX8uNInR2GRhK.jpg","original_title":"Morgan: Killer Doll","original_language":"en"},{"id":571785,"adult":false,"title":"Time to Hunt","video":false,"overview":"Four young men want to leave their dystopian world behind and go to a distant paradise to execute a money robbery, a daring act that will have unexpected consequences.","genre_ids":[18,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3583,"vote_count":339,"poster_path":"/bkuuvDoPkOJpg0ZDzHkUWt8ZG5A.jpg","release_date":"2020-02-22","vote_average":7.168,"backdrop_path":"/a8ppJJIQmEJcLSFfhxupc4aT4KW.jpg","original_title":"사냥의 시간","original_language":"ko"},{"id":84488,"adult":false,"title":"Cleopatra: Queen of Sex","video":false,"overview":"Three people from the future, who travel spiritually to the era of the Egyptian queen Cleopatra VII Philopator and her Roman lovers Julius Caesar and Mark Antony, become their closest friends as they try to unravel the nature of the plan developed in their own time by a sinister enemy.","genre_ids":[16,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6833,"vote_count":46,"poster_path":"/2Gt0jd8XR0NOxX0mq3dLXoPX75M.jpg","release_date":"1970-09-15","vote_average":5.707,"backdrop_path":"/s2zYVUHJJCexR1lehBav04DnJAJ.jpg","original_title":"クレオパトラ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1292531,"adult":false,"title":"Burning Sun: Exposing the Secret K-pop Chat Groups","video":false,"overview":"A BBCEye investigation into three K-pop stars who were sharing evidence of sexual crimes in secret chat groups.","genre_ids":[99,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2325,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/p7ThOmiV6mNubvoE2ar3CEKIoHY.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-19","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/Lu4ylOhkegm4TNZmDkVHEK67xD.jpg","original_title":"Burning Sun: Exposing the Secret K-pop Chat Groups","original_language":"en"},{"id":499191,"adult":false,"title":"Call Boy","video":false,"overview":"Ryo Morinaka is a university student and works part-time at a bar. He is bored with his daily life and exists in a state of torpor. One day, his friend Shinya Tajima brings the owner of a host bar over to the place where Ryo Morinaka works. Shizuka Mido is the owner of the host bar. Soon, Ryo Morinaka begins to work for Shizuka Mido at the members only host bar. He feels embarrassment initially, but he fulfills the desires of women and develops a sense of purpose.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.4582,"vote_count":54,"poster_path":"/3fVRb3uoRDjbA9X95C88FOJ0rlZ.jpg","release_date":"2018-04-06","vote_average":6.444,"backdrop_path":"/1p98ESRDKb3W1BS8GluxHvDDhRa.jpg","original_title":"娼年","original_language":"ja"},{"id":338276,"adult":false,"title":"In Their Room: London","video":false,"overview":"In Their Room (2009-present) is an on-going multi-city documentary series about gay men, bedrooms and intimacy. The series veers into the bedrooms of men where you see them doing everything from the most banal to the sometimes more erotic. Complimenting the revealing nature of their everyday activities are confessional interviews about fantasies, turn-ons and vulnerabilities.","g